{"tid":135123,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"地球四大言之鑿鑿嘅謊言及鳩嗡預測","createTime":"2017-02-26T06:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T11:33:58.000Z","uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ee987c7ef41735236727241a21ed5904a0edfa15","tid":135123,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:16:29.000Z","msg":"支爆<br />\n年年都話下年爆，爆左十年都未爆<br />\n<br />\n香港樂壇已死<br />\n由twins 出道已經講緊，講到twins 老死嗰日啲人應該仲嗡緊呢句野<br />\n<br />\n福島核事故失控<br />\n成日話日本啲人已經唔理，今次死撚硬，每日大規模核污染，但明明冇乜大鑊野爆出黎，啲核爆撚就會話人封鎖消息<br />\n<br />\n暖化<br />\n等巴打貼返乜鳩而家唔凍只係涼嗰篇潮文出黎<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097c77312787f3b2827a37580d574e129da100a8","tid":135123,"uid":79275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:22:36.000Z","msg":"正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ff8325b128b4071380396dc89ab62bd3455726","tid":135123,"uid":2974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:23:24.000Z","msg":"小朋友幹大姐姐"},{"pid":"cbda6755840c3cccd4ce478358b7b614ad9bead0","tid":135123,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"apple已死"},{"pid":"deab0194c06749c2537af166f93dc48cce61ce5d","tid":135123,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:24:55.000Z","msg":"利記下年拎英超"},{"pid":"4a031a8688f742de989ec6ee1ebf9daa03c7ee97","tid":135123,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:15:21.000Z","msg":"過年前有班仆行又話支爆<br />\n過唔到一月 仲要實牙實齒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b9996689599018ac212243d6b7607203cde9a7","tid":135123,"uid":79275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T09:23:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過年前有班仆行又話支爆<br />\n過唔到一月 仲要實牙實齒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港死都未爆"},{"pid":"9571aa84